      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3167_0061"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="org" ref="#pmb29442">Frankfurter Zeitung</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">(<rs type="org" ref="#pmb29442"><foreign xml:lang="fra">Gazette de Francfort</foreign></rs>).</hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><foreign xml:lang="fra">Fondateur M.</foreign><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb87771">L. Sonnemann</rs>.</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print">Journal politique, financier,</hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print">commercial et littéraire.</hi></foreign></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Paraissant trois fois par jour.</hi></hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs></hi>, <date when="1897-10-05">5. Oct.</date></seg></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Bureau à <rs type="place" ref="#pmb182">Paris</rs></hi></hi></foreign></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb43397">10 <hi rend="spaced-out">Rue de la
                                 Bourse</hi></rs>.</hi></hi></foreign></seg></opener><p>Ich bitte um eine kurze Nachricht, <salute>lieb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ter Freund</salute>.
               Kein langer Brief, nur ein paar Worte! Du weißt ja, daß <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02828-1"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard</rs></hi> nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreibt<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02828-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann</rs> galt als notorisch
                  unzuverlässiger Briefeschreiber.</note>. So muß ich mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon an Dich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t
               wenden, um etwas über Dich zu wi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en.</p><p>Sei herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t begrüßt!</p><closer>Dein <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmn</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
